messages.messageBody:
Andi,
I live in between Scott and Adrian. The nearest larger towns are Dublin
and Swainsboro. I am about an equal distance for both. I am about an 65
miles or so southeast of Macon. How far south of Atlanta are you?

At 10:15 AM 09/11/1999 -0400, you wrote:
> Cathy,
> We are south of Atlanta.
>Andi Cathy
>
